## Summary
This documentation explains how to build, analyze, and create cohorts from machine learning predictions in Amplitude Activation, covering the prediction creation workflow, audience analysis with percentile-based user segmentation, feature importance ranking, model performance metrics (AUC, log loss, true/false positive rates), and converting predictions into targetable cohorts for campaigns.

